      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "3883-3910",
      "markText": "她不由得判断：丈夫鹈原宪一和那个曾根益三郎是同一个人！",
      "totalCount": 234,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=3883&rangeEnd=3910",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=3883&rangeEnd=3910"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_5_6054-6101",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "6054-6101",
      "markText": "实际上，她并不认为自己有什么任性之处，只不过觉得假想式的自责会为自己平添一分小女人的可爱而已。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6054&rangeEnd=6101",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=6054&rangeEnd=6101"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_5_10141-10205",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "10141-10205",
      "markText": "她第一次体会到夫妻的离别之苦。 而这，是祯子最后一次看见自己的丈夫鹈原宪一。",
      "totalCount": 195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10141&rangeEnd=10205",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=10141&rangeEnd=10205"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_44_5221-5270",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "5221-5270",
      "markText": "“您也知道本多先生去东京出差了。可是，今天下午四点左右，金泽警察局收到消息说，本多先生忽然死了。”",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=5221&rangeEnd=5270",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=5221&rangeEnd=5270"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_35_2612-2640",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "2612-2640",
      "markText": "但当她的目光落在祯子身上时，却是一怔，再也无法移开视线。",
      "totalCount": 150,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=2612&rangeEnd=2640",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=2612&rangeEnd=2640"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_18_3965-4003",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "3965-4003",
      "markText": "啊！祯子终于想起来了，宪一夹在书里的两张照片中，有一张照的就是眼前这栋房子！",
      "totalCount": 130,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3965&rangeEnd=4003",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=3965&rangeEnd=4003"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_4_782-837",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "782-837",
      "markText": "她以女性的敏感觉察到，这类男性身上普遍欠缺一种坦荡的气概，不论是在身体方面还是在工作方面，他们都显得孱弱无能。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=782&rangeEnd=837",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=782&rangeEnd=837"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_4_3616-3637",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3616-3637",
      "markText": "祯子答应了这桩婚事后，就向公司提出了辞职。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3616&rangeEnd=3637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3616&rangeEnd=3637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_4_466-498",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "466-498",
      "markText": "祯子今年二十六岁，鹈原大她十岁，三十六岁，两人年龄上倒也算相称。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=466&rangeEnd=498",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=466&rangeEnd=498"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_5_3456-3487",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3456-3487",
      "markText": "祯子的眼睛噙满了泪水，这是决定结婚以来，第一个让她感动的时刻。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3456&rangeEnd=3487",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3456&rangeEnd=3487"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_7_2025-2122",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "2025-2122",
      "markText": "我看过一本外国小说，里面说有个男人，他在步入晚年时，不仅有足够的财产养老，孩子也都长大成人了，可以说生活全无后顾之忧，但为了寻求某种不一样的生活，他舍弃家庭离家出走了。我觉得他的心情可以理解。”",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2025&rangeEnd=2122",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=2025&rangeEnd=2122"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_11_3900-3929",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "3900-3929",
      "markText": "一个身穿和式外褂的男子与他们擦身而过，驻足回望他们的身影。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3900&rangeEnd=3929",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=3900&rangeEnd=3929"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_46_3561-3596",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "3561-3596",
      "markText": "宪一夹在田沼久子和祯子两个女人的爱之间，左右为难，最后走上了自杀之路。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3561&rangeEnd=3596",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=3561&rangeEnd=3596"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_61_5441-5496",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "5441-5496",
      "markText": "虽然战争已经结束十三年了，但是日本女性的伤口还没有完全愈合。只要受到一点冲击，从那旧伤口里还会喷出肮脏的血来。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=5441&rangeEnd=5496",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=5441&rangeEnd=5496"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_5_966-1016",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "966-1016",
      "markText": "当时在她听来，这不过是一位善于讲场面话的人普通的致辞，但是很久以后，她才从这些致辞中体会到某些真意。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=966&rangeEnd=1016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=966&rangeEnd=1016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_5_2529-2562",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2529-2562",
      "markText": "祯子忽然产生了一个奇怪的想法：上了这辆车，自己便踏上了人生的歧路。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2529&rangeEnd=2562",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2529&rangeEnd=2562"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_36_8834-8845",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "8834-8845",
      "markText": "有些事要明天才能出结果",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=8834&rangeEnd=8845",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=8834&rangeEnd=8845"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300103482_57_4990-5014",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "4990-5014",
      "markText": "X让宪一把现场布置好之后，便把他从崖上推了下去。",
      "totalCount": 96,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300103482&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=4990&rangeEnd=5014",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/91d32fe0813ab8eecg0129d6?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=4990&rangeEnd=5014"
    },
    {
